**Characteristics of the player's non-dominant side (Right-handed or Left-handed):**

- The player presents lower functional amplitude which means a lower quantity of rotational degrees;
- The greater the rotation amplitude, the greater acceleration capacity will be generated;
- The = and + polarity works as an acceleration catalyst;
