- Lateral Effect: Definition of racket entry into the ball associated with termination (Center Vector - Right);
- Pectoral Contraction and Extension;
- Time Reference: Clock framing and Time Sector Definition (1:00pm-2:00pm);
- Direction associated with Impact Point;
